text: Niscaya yisakale kupharai karaiche arau kaphiraraupe mrtyubarana karaiche sihamtara konoba'i prthirai bharaa sona binimayasbaraupa pradana karaile'o seya ketiya'o grahana karaa nahaâ€™ba.
